The paper addresses the problem of monocular depth estimation using a semi-supervised adversarial learning framework. This involves the use of CNNs and discriminators to achieve high performance with limited training data. Based on this, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is computer vision (cs.CV), followed by machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Robotics (cs.RO) and multimedia (cs.MM) are also possible categories, as they may involve applications of monocular depth estimation.
